Forcefully restarts Varnish in the remote server.
<em>Sample usage</em>
<pre class="sh_python">
    class MySampleRole(Role):
        def provision(self):
            with self.using(VarnishRole) as role:
                if not self.is_process_running('varnishd'):
                    role.restart()
</pre>

